Steps to Install and setup wifi acess point
First Install the install.sh file 
sudo chmod +x install.sh ap.sh //give the execute permission to both the files
sudo ./install.sh  //it will install modules and setup details

Second file ap.sh will use to setp wifiname and password
run the command 
ap wifiname wifipasswd
ap demo demo123

it will create the wifi access point and it work as hotsopt.
